&lt;div class=&quot;elementor-element elementor-element-e5f9ae2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor&quot; data-id=&quot;e5f9ae2&quot; data-element_type=&quot;widget&quot; data-widget_type=&quot;text-editor.default&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementor-widget-container&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced Process Engineer with experience in Composites Manufacturing. The ideal candidate will be responsible for developing, optimizing, and controlling manufacturing processes used to fabricate composite components.&amp;nbsp; This role ensures consistent product quality, reduced process variability, increases throughput, and supports continuous improvement activities across our company.&amp;nbsp; The candidate should be able to review technical data and generate technical summaries to be shared with senior stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementor-element elementor-element-74eb47b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot; data-id=&quot;74eb47b&quot; data-element_type=&quot;widget&quot; data-widget_type=&quot;text-editor.default&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementor-widget-container&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and improve potential manufacturing processes to increase efficiency, reduce costs, and and improve product quality (eg/ VARTM, infusion, prepreg...).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementToProof&quot;&gt;Create process parameters and control plans.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementToProof&quot;&gt;Conduct Design of Experiments, capability studies, and CT analyses.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct root cause analysis and troubleshoot process issues to identify and implement effective solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement process improvements, including design changes, equipment modifications, and process control enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;elementToProof&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain SOPs, WIs, visual aids, and training materials.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare technical reports that document process changes, test results, and quality issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze technical data and generate technical summaries for senior stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including production, service, quality, and R&amp;amp;D, to drive continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date on the latest industry trends and advancements in process engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical support for field team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in the filed as needed to identify and implement process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide technical support for production issues and process changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with environmental, health, and safety (EHS) regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and maintain process documentation, including work instructions, process flow diagrams, and control plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in new product development and launch activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
