&lt;p&gt;Lead and manage projects related to wind turbine blade design, development, testing, and manufacturing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure that all aspects of the composite design and manufacturing process are efficient and effective.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop and implement new materials, processes, and technology for wind turbine turbines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including production, quality, and R&amp;amp;D, to drive continuous improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct root cause analysis and troubleshoot process issues to identify and implement effective solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perform time studies and cycle time analysis to optimize manufacturing processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Analyze and interpret technical data to identify trends, issues, and opportunities for improvement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ensure compliance with environmental, health, and safety (EHS) regulations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
